cellmate.accumulo.writer.dbtransformers
Class AccumuloDBItemTransformers

Object
  AccumuloDBItemTransformers

@Beta
public class AccumuloDBItemTransformers
extends Object

Static helper methods that build DBItemTransformers to generate Mutations from Cell groups. At this time this is untested.

mapStringValueToQualWhenColFamMatched

public static <C> DBItemTransformer<Mutation,C> mapStringValueToQualWhenColFamMatched(Set<String> colFamsToWriteValueAsQual)
Takes a map of column family keys and for any cells with matching column families, lookup the desired qualifier for the key. If column family does not match, write label as qualifier.

Type Parameters:

Parameters:
colFamsToWriteValueAsQual - map of column families and desired label for each.
